reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ultimate Athleisure Accessory
reviews.reviewText: I am absolutely thrilled with this du-pe Lulu-lem0n belt bag! Not only does it offer the same stylish and sporty vibe as the original, but it comes at a fraction of the price. The quality of the materials used is surprisingly impressive, making it feel sturdy and durable.The design is incredibly versatile, allowing my niece to wear it around her waist or across her chest – perfect for both rugged and casual outings. The adjustable straps ensure a comfortable fit for all body types, and the zippered compartments provide ample space for essentials like keys, phone, wallet, and even a small water bottle...or in my nieces case, lip gloss, nail polish, hair scrunchies, and a juice box.One of the standout features of this du-pe is its thoughtful organization. The interior pockets help me keep my belongings neatly separated and easily accessible. The zippers glide smoothly and haven't snagged once, which is a pleasant surprise for a bag in this price range.I also appreciate the attention to detail in the stitching and overall construction of the bag. It's evident that the manufacturers took their time to replicate the premium look and feel of the original Lulu-lem0n version.We received numerous compliments on this bag, with friends and even strangers asking where we got it. It's a testament to how close this du-pe comes to the real thing. For anyone who loves athleisure fashion but doesn't want to break the bank, I wholeheartedly recommend this belt bag. It's a fantastic accessory that combines style, functionality, and affordability in one package.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Simple and perfect
reviews.reviewText: Even if this only lasted for the one vacation I used it for so far, it would still have been worth it for the price - but I expect it to last. Kept the essentials right at hand, so lightweight it didn't feel like wearing a thing, easy zippers, small enough to throw in a beach bag or larger backpack, the strap adjusts quickly and easily, etc. The back zip pocket is great for a standard phone, the main pocket easily fits a small wallet, keys, a lippy or two, and a travel pack of tissues. The only small improvement I could think of would be to add a zip or velcro to one of the interior sections for something like a single key you don't want to slip out on accident. But there are other ways to manage those little problems so no big deal. Oh and the tabs on the two zippers are pretty jingle-y together, which doesn't both me but might other people.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: OMG, this fanny pack is soooo roomy! reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a really nice little bag. The strap and zipper are very strong and durable, the nylon exterior will be easy to keep clean. It's large enough to easily hold my Pixel 8 Pro phone and keys and a few other things that I need. The strap is adjustable from tiny to jumbo. Plus, it arrived before they promised.

reviews.reviewText: Very good quality. Great price.. Clip is very sturdy and doesn’t unsnap easily. I was surprised that I was able to fit my phone along with a many other things in this bag. Very convenient.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars High quality and beautiful color but annoying zipper jingle
reviews.reviewText: Bought this to take on a trip. Unfortunately it was slightly too small for what I hoped to use it for. My sunglasses took up the majority of the space and I couldn’t also fit my medication and phone charger in and zip it up, so I’ll be returning it.Pros: well made, beautiful orchid purple color, smooth running zippersCons: zipper pulls jangled against each other in a really annoying way. Slightly too small for what I needed. As a plus size lady I had to open the strap all the way to wear it crossbody. It did fit but was a little snug.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Color is pretty and quality seems good. I love it's a double zipper too. Just the right size. Not too small not too big. Can't fit wallet, keys and cell phone with room to spare.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: For the price, this is a steal. The belt feels like such high quality, the pouch itself holds a lot and it still has pockets to separate stuff. I love it. Some reviews show the strap ripping but in my opinion if your pouch is being weighed down causing that to happen then just buy a purse. This is for essentials not for someone who needs random extra stuff on the go. The zipper pieces are a bit loud because they are heavier duty but I don’t notice it too much out and about.
Práctica y muy bonita. De buena calidad.

Me base en los comentarios y la verdad si esta muy bonita. Es practica. Me gusta mucho el cierre grueso, ya que evita que no se atore. Había visto otras bolsas parecidas a esta pero no me convencía los cierres. La calidad si es muy buena. Compraría otra bolsa en otro color.
Gran calidad muy igual a lululemon.

reviews.reviewTitle: Si quieren cangurera, es ésta.. No busquen otra
reviews.reviewText: Me encantó. El material se siente de muy buena calidad, el nylon no está delgadito ni nada y la correa y cierres también se ven muy resistentes y lindos. Es chica, pero le cabe mas de lo que te esperas (como referencia puede caber una cartera grande de esas donde los billetes van estirados pero no entraría nada más, más que unas llaves o algo así pequeño en la bolsita trasera). Y algo que me sorprendió muy gratamente es que trae una etiqueta donde dice que esta hecha con materiales reciclados y hasta el paquetito con bolitas para humedad es sustentable. De verdad quedé fascinada con la compra. No gasten en lululemon 🤭
La calidad es excelente, le cabe un celular grande, llaves, dinero, tarjetas, perfecta para llevar lo esencial 10/10, fue para un regalo y le gusto mucho
